## 7. Architecture: Box Model (from docs/SCENARIO_SYSTEM.mx)

The system is organized into distinct "Boxes" that communicate via events:

| Box | Component | Status | Notes |
|-----|-----------|--------|-------|
| A | GameState | ✅ Complete | Single source of truth for all state |
| B | MergeController | ✅ Complete | Core loop pacing, merge availability |
| C | GotchiSim + DriversController | ✅ Complete | Affection/mercy drivers, grime, collapse detection |
| D | StorySequencer + ScenarioDirector | ✅ Complete | Event/Scenario/Sequence system (refactored in b1dd1cf) |
| E | Ending System | ⚠️ INCOMPLETE | Logic exists (drivers, survival tracking) but display/rendering missing |

### Box C: Simulation Reducer (GotchiSim)
| Feature | Status | Details |
|---------|--------|---------|
| Sleep metronome | ✅ Complete | Drains 0.02/s while in Gotchi mode; forces merge at 0 |
| Affection driver | ✅ Complete | Warmth actions (pet) drive affection gain |
| Mercy driver | ✅ Complete | Hygiene actions (wash/groom) + merge timing drive mercy |
| Grime creep | ✅ Complete | Increases with neglect, reduced by care actions |
| Collapse detection | ✅ Complete | Triggers when deathEnabled and needs hit threshold |

### Box D: Story Sequencer (refactored in b1dd1cf)
| Feature | Status | Details |
|---------|--------|---------|
| Sequence selection | ✅ Complete | ScenarioDirector.SelectSequence() returns {scene, scenarioId} steps |
| Merge-in/merge-out phases | ✅ Complete | Phase enum tracks position in sequence |
| Event handling | ✅ Complete | StoryBeatStarted -> play sequence -> StoryBeatCompleted |
| Climax handling | ✅ Complete | DeathEnabled flag set at climax step |

### Box B: Merge Controller
| Feature | Status | Details |
|---------|--------|---------|
| First merge timing bucket | ✅ Complete | Immediate/AfterABit/AfterNeglect based on wait time + needs |
| Merge lock cooldown | ✅ Complete | 3 seconds after each beat |
| Voluntary merge gate | ✅ Complete | VOLUNTARY_MERGE_UNLOCKED flag controls early merges |
| Forced merge | ✅ Complete | When sleep hits 0 |

